This is the README file for episoder by Stefan Ott
Get the latest version at http://tools.desire.ch/episoder/
===============================================================================

PURPOSE
=======
episoder is a tool to tell you about new episodes of your favourite TV shows.


CONFIGURATION
=============
See "man episoder"


INSTALLATION
============
    * Run ./install.sh install [base_dir] where base_dir is the directory you want
      episoder to be installed under (e.g. /usr or /usr/local).
    * Create a cron job to have your database rebuilt once a day
    * Add "$base_dir/bin/episoder showlist" (e.g. /usr/bin/episoder showlist)
      to your ~/.bashrc, ~/.bash_profile, /etc/bash.bashrc or /etc/profile.
      Consult the bash docs to find out which file you want to use.


CONTACT
=======
If you find any bugs or have any idea of how to improve this tool, please
use the bug tracker of the forum on our website.
